gate: LOCKED
sprint: S04
track: C
task: C5
title: "test(parts-schematics): per-brand fixture coverage for schematic parsers (#1453)"
repos: [crop-front]
priority: P3
refs:
  - CROP-front#1453
requires: [TYPESCRIPT]

description: |
  Schematic parsers lack per-brand fixture coverage — a parser regression for a
  specific brand goes undetected until prod. Add fixture files and test cases
  covering each brand's schematic format so parser changes are caught in CI.

scope:
  in:
    - Identify brands with schematic data and without existing parser fixtures
    - Add minimal fixture file per missing brand (real or anonymised sample)
    - Add vitest test per brand: parse fixture → assert expected BOM shape
  out:
    - Changing parser logic
    - Adding fixtures for brands already covered

acceptance:
  - Every brand with schematic data has at least one parser fixture + test
  - All new tests green in CI

dep: none
output: test fixtures + vitest tests per brand
